<li><a href="http://www.aaronbell.com/lets-make-salt-minions-on-digitalocean/" rel="nofollow">Create an army of Salt minions on DigitalOcean</a> - Combine the simplicity of Salt with DigitalOcean's snapshot and image feature.</li>
