<li><a href="https://github.com/maerteijn/SaltGUI">SaltGUI</a> - A web interface for managing SaltStack based infrastructure.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/webedia-dev/pepperboard">Pepperboard</a> - A simple and modular dashboard toolkit for SaltStack.</li>
</ul>
